We're waiting; we're having a lot of technical issues.

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:38.046
That's why I'm late.

00:01:38.046 --> 00:01:42.360
That's why I usually do not announce when I'm coming on here live.

00:01:49.257 --> 00:01:49.629
The enemy does not like this prayer time, obviously.

00:01:52.700 --> 00:01:53.240
And so, I'm not frustrated.

