You know, it's exciting when you know you're poking them in the eye.

00:02:04.860 --> 00:02:18.200
But we've had a lot of stuff going on with all our internet and our cameras and everything else, so it's been a little bit of a hiccup here today.

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:20.088
So, is it working now?

00:02:20.088 --> 00:02:20.904
Everything's good?

00:02:20.904 --> 00:02:21.448
800?

00:02:21.448 --> 00:02:22.800
Okay, good.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:25.325
Well, praise the Lord.

00:02:25.325 --> 00:02:31.297
Well, good afternoon, good evening, and good night, whatever, wherever you are in the world.

00:02:31.297 --> 00:02:34.333
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:02:34.333 --> 00:02:36.187
We're going to just take right off.

00:02:38.368 --> 00:02:39.720
I don't have a lot of time here now because I'm a little behind.

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:43.160
So, I'm going to just get right into it and pray with y'all.

00:02:43.160 --> 00:03:01.623
Yesterday when we were praying, the glory of the Lord filled our hotel room, and it was—I told Braden, we all felt it—it was the peace that passes all understanding, just that weightiness of the presence of God filled this room.

00:03:17.204 --> 00:03:17.507
And I was surprised, honestly.

00:03:17.507 --> 00:03:28.360
I mean, you're in a hotel that's not your house and, you know, on the road like this, and the glory of the Lord shows up like that.

00:03:45.160 --> 00:03:45.655
I was just in awe at just the presence of the Lord, and it was just exciting that the Lord would visit like that.

00:03:45.655 --> 00:03:55.120
We've been at the prayer conference and praying over what they feel led to pray over concerning America and things like that.

00:04:07.959 --> 00:04:08.261
But my heart is going to tell you this: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:04:08.261 --> 00:04:09.773
You must know this.

00:04:09.773 --> 00:04:15.915
You must have an urgency about our Father's return.

00:04:15.915 --> 00:04:22.087
It is time that the body of Christ has urgency and wakes up.

00:04:29.335 --> 00:04:31.660
We are in the last of the last of the last seconds before the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:04:32.930 --> 00:04:34.180
We see the wars and the rumors of wars.

00:04:35.835 --> 00:04:37.571
We see Israel and what's going on with Israel, watching the fig tree.

00:04:37.571 --> 00:04:45.890
But as we pray today, the enemy within—we'll just pick up where we left off yesterday with the terrorist attacks.

00:05:01.200 --> 00:05:01.880
I know what the Lord is showing me.

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:08.790
They were picking up on some of it today concerning July the 4th of this year because it's an anniversary year.

00:05:08.790 --> 00:05:09.880
It's the big celebration.

00:05:10.787 --> 00:05:16.533
I think it's 200 and some years or whatever it is, the 250th for the United States of America.

00:05:16.533 --> 00:05:19.263
But what I'm picking up on is way before July of 2026.

00:05:19.263 --> 00:05:22.617
We must pray for our elections in 2026 for sure.

00:05:40.415 --> 00:05:40.650
This is a major hot spot for everything that I'm getting concerning November of next year.

00:05:40.650 --> 00:05:44.870
This time next year, I pray we've already prayed this thing through.

00:06:00.760 --> 00:06:01.080
We don't need to be coming up to the wire and praying it through; we need to tackle this thing now.

00:06:07.902 --> 00:06:14.940
The elections of 2026, if we do not keep the Senate and the House and get some better judges in our nation, it won't do any good to even have the presidency.

00:06:14.940 --> 00:06:24.995
We must keep the Senate with more of a majority and the House to push through some of the things that I have seen.

00:06:24.995 --> 00:06:30.380
Now, I believe that we have—there's power in numbers, there's power in prayer.

00:06:37.925 --> 00:06:38.250
And it's so exciting to meet some of you all.

00:06:41.503 --> 00:06:44.126
I met some people from Sweden today, some from Mexico, and another man who just saw me.

00:06:48.320 --> 00:06:48.670
I said, "Are you here for the prayer conference?

00:06:48.670 --> 00:06:53.343
" He said, "No, I just came here for a vacation.

00:06:56.093 --> 00:06:58.200
" You know, Branson, Missouri is a major hot spot for vacation for a lot of people.

00:07:10.479 --> 00:07:10.760
And Sister Billie said that today, that an average of 8 million people come through here every single year.

00:07:20.827 --> 00:07:21.160
And when I was driving around today, the Lord said, "I told you this.

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:23.980
" He said, "I'm getting it ready for the revival.

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:26.092
Do you remember what I said?

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:28.728
" I said, "Yes, Lord, you picked a good spot.

00:07:28.728 --> 00:07:30.024
8 million visitors a year.

00:07:39.880 --> 00:07:40.255
" And she said, "That's more people that visit here than visit Israel.

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:53.832
" And I was like, "That's amazing for this little bitty town, that we have more visitors come here in this little area in Branson, Missouri than Israel has in all of the tourist season of Israel in a whole entire single year.

00:07:53.832 --> 00:07:54.850
" That's amazing.

00:07:54.850 --> 00:08:03.893
So, it shows why the Lord picked Branson, Missouri for a major revival, because there's already all these people coming here.

00:08:14.135 --> 00:08:14.410
So, He picked a hot spot in America.

00:08:14.410 --> 00:08:20.227
He said, "I choose to pick the central part of America on the New Madrid fault.

00:08:20.227 --> 00:08:30.231
This is going to be a major place for a major shaking to awaken, and a great revival will come to Branson, Missouri.

00:08:30.231 --> 00:08:40.335
" And as I was driving around today, the roads were so congested with so many people coming here for fall break, I just thought, you know, like Sister Billie always says, "Oh, what a plan.

00:08:40.335 --> 00:08:41.253
Oh, what a planner.

00:08:48.326 --> 00:08:48.554
" And I'm telling you all, I have such high expectations.

00:08:50.540 --> 00:09:03.954
I can, as I'm in the exact spot where I've always seen the visions looking out over where the sun is setting, looking out and the Lord's saying, "Brandon, this dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:09:11.063 --> 00:09:11.337
The ark door is closing.

00:09:11.337 --> 00:09:12.680
Jesus is coming.

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:15.387
" Do you understand, ladies and gentlemen?

00:09:15.387 --> 00:09:17.820
We're about to have the greatest harvest of souls.

00:09:28.507 --> 00:09:28.849
And I say that all the time, but I want to be that steady drum that keeps warning you about what's coming.

00:09:28.849 --> 00:09:32.120
So, we see Zelensky in the White House today asking for Tomahawks.

00:09:44.920 --> 00:09:45.173
And I said, "This is not a coincidence.

00:09:45.173 --> 00:09:48.640
" I saw this way before they are even talking about this, folks.

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:53.860
And here President Trump—oh, and then Putin had the meeting there saying, "We need to talk about this.

00:09:53.860 --> 00:09:56.902
We don't want those long-range missiles coming into Moscow.

00:09:56.902 --> 00:10:00.989
" And the reach was way beyond Moscow for what these missiles are able to do.

00:10:06.910 --> 00:10:11.653
But Zelensky was putting a demand on the relationship with the United States of America stating that he wanted long-range missiles to go way deep into Russia, and we don't want that.

00:10:11.653 --> 00:10:15.960
So, that's why we're praying, because I believe prayer changes things.

00:10:15.960 --> 00:10:23.069
But it is important that we realize that we are going to avert World War III in a great capacity in some areas.

00:10:23.069 --> 00:10:24.820
Now, can we stop the whole thing?

00:10:24.820 --> 00:10:25.330
No.

00:10:25.330 --> 00:10:27.640
But I believe we can stop some of it.

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:36.229
We can cause some peace in some of it, maybe delay some of it, I don't know.

00:10:36.229 --> 00:10:42.360
But the Lord said some of this stuff is going to happen because His Word said it would.

00:10:42.360 --> 00:10:58.944
So, we see these things happening in the news and what they're talking about, and I'm like—I told Diana, I said, "You know what's amazing to me is whenever you're seeing it in prayer weeks before, and then you start seeing it in the news weeks after, right?

00:10:59.831 --> 00:11:00.538
" And you just go, "Wow, Lord.

00:11:00.538 --> 00:11:01.009
Wow.

00:11:01.009 --> 00:11:01.480
Wow.

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:06.960
Nothing happens on this earth before He reveals it to His servants, the prophets, and I believe the watchmen of this generation.

00:11:06.960 --> 00:11:08.640
" He said, "I'm bringing in my closers.

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:11.853
" And He keeps bringing that up to me.

00:11:11.853 --> 00:11:13.000
It's time for impartation.

00:11:13.000 --> 00:11:14.280
You know what was interesting?

00:11:14.653 --> 00:11:17.516
I felt to talk to one of the key head prayer people, Sister Lynne.

00:11:19.560 --> 00:11:23.768
And I told D, I said, "I feel I just would like her to pray for us because she's a general.

00:11:23.768 --> 00:11:26.191
She's been—she's taught us prayer our whole entire lives.

00:11:26.191 --> 00:11:29.376
I mean, since we were little kids walking around, you know, barely in diapers.

00:11:29.376 --> 00:11:37.610
" And it was an honor that she would even talk to us, and she's excited because she says she watches our channel and stuff.

00:11:41.485 --> 00:11:41.760
And she laid hands on Diana.

00:11:51.140 --> 00:11:51.400
And I've never seen the power of God move on my wife like that other than when we've been at some Billy Burke meetings.

00:11:51.400 --> 00:12:01.472
But my wife's hand shook under the power of God, which I don't understand why, but it shook under the power of God.

00:12:01.472 --> 00:12:15.660
Now, usually it's always the whole being—you can feel it and it goes in you—but her right hand, where Sister Lyn Hammond prayed for my wife and grabbed a hold of her hand, shook for over an hour and she couldn't control it.

00:12:20.640 --> 00:12:21.147
It was just under the power of God.

00:12:21.147 --> 00:12:28.573
Her whole arm was; she could feel it from her fingers all the way up to her shoulder.

00:12:28.573 --> 00:12:30.360
Come and tell them.

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:31.960
You're sitting here.

00:12:39.947 --> 00:12:40.173
You tell them.

00:12:40.400 --> 00:12:41.949
I ain't going to steal her thunder.

00:12:41.949 --> 00:12:43.430
Here, you can sit on my lap.

00:12:45.720 --> 00:12:46.017
You want to sit right here?

00:12:51.040 --> 00:12:51.227
I don't have to—you told it really good.

00:12:52.533 --> 00:12:52.689
I know.

00:12:52.689 --> 00:12:54.760
Can you see her?

00:12:54.760 --> 00:12:56.520
All right.

00:12:56.520 --> 00:12:57.120
Tell them.

00:12:57.120 --> 00:12:57.520
Yeah.

00:12:57.520 --> 00:13:04.687
Whenever she laid hands on us and prayed, she put her hand right here on my arm.

00:13:11.700 --> 00:13:11.947
And when she did, I felt the power of God go into my arm.

00:13:12.193 --> 00:13:15.063
And it went all the way from here to my elbow.

00:13:21.863 --> 00:13:22.200
And it traveled.

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:25.300
It kind of stopped right there, but it was all through my hand.

00:13:28.556 --> 00:13:28.911
And I just felt it vibrating like a vibration, like a current.

00:13:30.307 --> 00:13:33.440
And I was watching my hand, and I was like—she was praying and I was feeling it—and I was thinking, 'Wow, this is like my hand.

00:13:42.600 --> 00:13:42.800
I can feel the power of God.

00:13:42.800 --> 00:13:45.615
' And I was just weeping.

00:13:48.820 --> 00:13:55.320
And then she put her hand up here on my shoulder, and I felt it come all the way down my arm clear to my elbow, and it went all the way up and down.

00:13:55.320 --> 00:14:03.827
My whole hand was just under the power for over an hour.

00:14:03.827 --> 00:14:05.250
It was like being electrocuted.

00:14:05.250 --> 00:14:05.830
Yes.

00:14:07.507 --> 00:14:09.320
And it really was amazing because I've never seen you do that.

00:14:10.040 --> 00:14:12.360
And even our littlest was like, 'Daddy, can Mommy control her hand?

00:14:12.360 --> 00:14:17.446
' Because Paisley was just staring at it, you know, because her mom's hand was sitting there just shaking.

00:14:21.550 --> 00:14:21.840
And it was just amazing to see that.

00:14:31.863 --> 00:14:32.120
I knew there was impartation—there's something, because that's just not normal for us.

00:14:34.609 --> 00:14:34.938
And we don't put on—we ain't here for a show.

00:14:51.270 --> 00:14:51.765
We don't care.

00:14:51.765 --> 00:15:01.257
You know, it's like to us, we're just Brandon and Diana, you know, and there's no performance.

00:15:20.040 --> 00:15:20.360
You get what you get.

00:15:20.360 --> 00:15:23.460
I'm not here to try to entertain you.

00:15:25.180 --> 00:15:26.634
And that's why I've always maintained that.

00:15:26.634 --> 00:15:27.823
Keep being authentic.

00:15:27.823 --> 00:15:33.783
No matter how much it gets bigger, don't try to be a performance.

00:15:37.627 --> 00:15:37.880
There is no time for performance.

00:15:45.034 --> 00:15:45.246
It's fake.

00:15:45.246 --> 00:15:46.640
I don't like fake Christianity.

00:15:46.640 --> 00:15:48.578
I don't like fake Holy Ghost stuff.

00:15:48.578 --> 00:15:52.280
No, I want the real, authentic move and touch of the power of God.

00:15:55.105 --> 00:15:58.710
And if it's not, I don't want it at all.

00:15:58.710 --> 00:16:00.606
I'm not here, you know.

00:16:03.413 --> 00:16:03.680
I see some people and you think, 'Is that real?

00:16:03.680 --> 00:16:04.569
Is that whatever?

00:16:04.569 --> 00:16:23.338
' And I don't try to judge them, but I'm saying there are a lot of times you realize that their flesh is involved more than the spirit, you know, and I'm just like, 'I don't want to be one of those.

00:16:23.338 --> 00:16:38.016
' But I realize when my wife is getting a touch from the Lord, and it's authentic, because Diana is a no-nonsense person.

00:16:39.914 --> 00:16:41.097
And so, it's the same with me.

00:16:41.097 --> 00:16:43.390
I'm a no-nonsense person.

00:16:51.320 --> 00:16:51.560
I don't play Holy Ghost.

00:16:51.560 --> 00:16:52.280
It's either real or it's not.

00:17:02.080 --> 00:17:02.355
And because I see, I don't give any courtesy falls.

00:17:02.355 --> 00:17:09.733
If the power of God's not there to knock me on my heinie, I don't want it, you know.

00:17:09.733 --> 00:17:11.629
I'll resist it more than anything.

00:17:16.620 --> 00:17:18.255
And so I just say, 'Hey,' because I'm not going to let you push me down, either—'Holy Ghost push.

00:17:18.255 --> 00:17:30.160
' You know, people try to push you down in the name of the power of God and try to make you go down, and you're like, 'No, that's not the power of God.

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:32.400
That's you knocking me down with your hand.

00:17:32.400 --> 00:17:33.300
Stop with your nonsense.

00:17:33.300 --> 00:17:39.411
' But I'm just saying, you know when the Lord is authentically touching somebody, and my wife got a touch today, and I was so thankful for that.

00:17:44.680 --> 00:17:45.046
I told her, I said, 'We're Holy Ghost junkies.

00:17:45.046 --> 00:17:47.554
We're going to find the authentic.

00:17:47.554 --> 00:17:52.427
' And Sister Lynn touched Diana today, and it was pretty awesome.

00:18:01.613 --> 00:18:02.004
So I just wanted to tell you all that, you know.

00:18:02.004 --> 00:18:03.569
Love you, baby.

00:18:03.569 --> 00:18:04.646
So pretty cool.

00:18:04.646 --> 00:18:06.434
That's not you.

00:18:06.434 --> 00:18:09.000
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

00:18:09.000 --> 00:18:23.303
You get the anointing of push on you, and they ain't going to have the anointing of push, and they start going, and you go, 'That's not the anointing of the Holy Ghost.

00:18:23.303 --> 00:18:25.627
You're trying to push people down.

00:18:25.627 --> 00:18:31.434
' And they give you a courtesy fall because you're pushing their head off.

00:18:31.434 --> 00:18:33.600
But I just like, you know, I want authentic.

00:18:38.840 --> 00:18:50.040
And there has been something authentic in our life, and we've touched it and tasted it, and I'm telling you, the Holy Spirit is real, and it puts a bad taste in some people's mouths whenever it's not.

00:18:50.040 --> 00:18:55.589
Now, I get off on that because I come across people and they say, 'Well, is this real?

00:18:55.589 --> 00:18:56.526
Is it?

00:18:56.526 --> 00:18:57.669
Is it not?

00:18:57.669 --> 00:18:59.611
' And I'm telling you, it's real.

00:18:59.611 --> 00:19:03.960
When I've been prayed for by Billy Burke, you can't stand; the glory comes in.

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:10.754
And last night when we had the move of God, Max, who is an Arab-American now—he got radically saved—was a Palestinian, right?

00:19:20.500 --> 00:19:21.080
Is that right?

00:19:21.080 --> 00:19:32.691
He saw Jesus walking around in the auditorium, and I knew it was authentic because of the way he said it.

00:19:32.691 --> 00:19:39.533
Now, not every vision do I believe; when somebody says they're seeing things, I just go, 'Whatever.

00:19:39.533 --> 00:19:42.600
' But this man I know is authentic.

00:19:42.600 --> 00:19:52.160
His name is Max, and he said he saw Jesus walking around last night in the service.

00:19:52.160 --> 00:19:54.027
But you could feel it.

00:20:03.446 --> 00:20:03.840
You could feel the tangible presence of God last night.

00:20:03.840 --> 00:20:06.780
Diana and I were in there.

00:20:06.780 --> 00:20:08.000
We could see the mist.

00:20:19.400 --> 00:20:23.860
And, like I said, I don't try to get all hyper-spiritual about stuff.

00:20:23.860 --> 00:20:25.453
If it's there, it's there.

00:20:25.453 --> 00:20:28.031
If it's not, it's not.

00:20:42.223 --> 00:20:42.509
And it was there.

00:20:42.509 --> 00:20:43.629
It was the same.

00:20:43.629 --> 00:20:53.651
Diana said it wasn't as thick as what we saw in the tent last year at this meeting when we went to the mountain and we went out there.

00:20:53.651 --> 00:21:01.570
They have the fish fry and all the things that are on Monday, and that's when the Holy Spirit was so strong.

00:21:01.570 --> 00:21:06.640
We even saw it; it was so thick you couldn't see through it—the glory cloud.

00:21:06.640 --> 00:21:14.400
Last night, we started worshiping, and the glory of the Lord came in, and it was tangible.

00:21:19.387 --> 00:21:19.920
Now, I didn't see Jesus, but Max did, and I think another man.

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:33.914
Right.

00:21:33.914 --> 00:21:39.133
So, he was walking around the aisles examining the troops, examining his children.

00:21:43.154 --> 00:21:44.947
And when we were up there and they were worshiping, they started singing the song.

00:21:50.324 --> 00:21:57.549
And she started singing, and the glory of the Lord came into the building, and, ladies and gentlemen, I kid you not, you could see a mist in the atmosphere.

00:21:57.549 --> 00:22:01.680
There was a heavy dew; you could feel it.

00:22:01.680 --> 00:22:11.271
Now, I don't know if everybody could see it, but there were quite a few that said they did, and you could feel the presence—the tangible presence of God.

00:22:15.880 --> 00:22:16.360
And I'm all about it.

00:22:30.160 --> 00:22:30.480
I told Sister Billie today, I said, 'I could park myself in a meeting like that and never leave.

00:22:30.480 --> 00:22:38.460
' People were—she told everybody they could go home because it was already so late, and people didn't want to leave.

00:22:38.460 --> 00:22:41.680
Some of them left, which I think—they missed out big time.

00:22:50.823 --> 00:22:51.577
The people who left, I just don't, honest to goodness, I don't know how you can leave a service and say, 'Well, I'm going home to go to bed.

00:22:51.577 --> 00:22:53.480
' What else is there to stay up for?

00:22:53.480 --> 00:23:02.240
If God's there and the glory cloud's there, you couldn't pay me a million dollars to want to leave that.

00:23:08.010 --> 00:23:11.160
I mean, seriously, the tangible presence of God is in the building, folks, and you want to go lay on your pillow?

00:23:11.160 --> 00:23:13.229
Forget it.

00:23:19.505 --> 00:23:20.360
I mean, there ain't nothing in this world—that's all that I'm living for is the presence and the glory.

00:23:32.731 --> 00:23:32.960
So, we could feel it.

00:23:32.960 --> 00:23:38.296
You could feel the tangible presence, and you could feel the weightiness of his presence.

00:23:38.296 --> 00:23:49.800
But like I said, Max was blessed with the vision of it, to see the Lord Jesus walking around looking at people.

00:24:03.258 --> 00:24:03.476
Some people were experiencing angels and things like that, but it was more that didn't than did.

00:24:11.595 --> 00:24:11.950
But the glory, everybody—I think you would have to be spiritually dead not to feel it.

00:24:19.360 --> 00:24:19.920
I mean seriously, the atmosphere was tangible—the presence of God.

00:24:19.920 --> 00:24:25.100
I'm so grateful, so thankful to experience the glory, so grateful.

00:24:25.100 --> 00:24:30.180
There is nothing like it, there's nothing like it.

00:24:42.880 --> 00:24:47.693
And for all the people who traveled—they had people from, like I said, South Korea, they had people from China, they had people from all over the globe.

00:24:53.667 --> 00:24:54.080
They brought them up today and were talking about it.

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:07.190
It was so cool to see so many people came from so many different places.

00:25:07.190 --> 00:25:09.050
And the people from Switzerland.

00:25:09.050 --> 00:25:11.074
Two different people from Switzerland.

00:25:11.074 --> 00:25:14.410
And I didn't realize there are that many different dialects in Switzerland.

00:25:14.410 --> 00:25:17.032
German, Italian, French—three different languages in different sectors.

00:25:17.228 --> 00:25:18.012
I didn't realize that.

00:25:18.012 --> 00:25:23.360
So we had the French represented here, and we had the Germans, from what I understood.

00:25:23.360 --> 00:25:26.973
So I thought, 'Well, praise God.

00:25:26.973 --> 00:25:34.810
' But really, really beautiful, really beautiful what the Lord is doing, but I'm expecting even more.

00:25:43.550 --> 00:25:44.160
You know, I know there's more.

00:25:44.160 --> 00:25:46.860
I know there's more.

00:25:57.577 --> 00:25:57.754
And I believe we are just entering in—first the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation.

00:25:57.754 --> 00:26:04.103
I believe for this revival that we're experiencing, I believe we're just entering into it.

00:26:17.120 --> 00:26:17.450
You can just barely see that blade coming up out of the ground for what's about to happen.

00:26:17.450 --> 00:26:19.430
It's just barely peeking through.

00:26:25.745 --> 00:26:28.160
You know, when you just get that seed, that little hatchling, the little seed is just barely poking itself through the soil.

00:26:37.000 --> 00:26:37.187
And I believe even like, you know, some people are talking about a turning point and all this stuff.

00:26:37.187 --> 00:26:41.240
Yes, but there's something so much more coming on the edge of time.

00:26:55.160 --> 00:26:55.420
All the stuff that's happening, folks, I'm telling you, we are right there.

00:26:55.420 --> 00:27:05.400
I even told Pastor Chip, one of the pastors, I told him, 'We've got to stop saying it's coming and start saying it's here.

00:27:05.400 --> 00:27:09.897
' And he said that's exactly what the Lord was telling him.

00:27:09.897 --> 00:27:13.740
But I believe when we start saying it's here, the glory is here.

00:27:14.260 --> 00:27:16.820
The glory and the manifested presence of the Lord is here.

00:27:16.820 --> 00:27:17.920
It's not coming.

00:27:27.916 --> 00:27:28.554
We're not going to experience it later on.

00:27:28.554 --> 00:27:34.240
Because if it's always coming, something is coming all the time.

00:27:34.240 --> 00:27:42.867
But I started thinking, get the mindset of expectation for the manifestation now.

00:27:42.867 --> 00:27:45.097
Why is it always tomorrow?

00:27:45.097 --> 00:27:49.150
It's like believing God always for tomorrow for your deliverance, for your marriage to get better.

00:27:49.150 --> 00:27:51.080
'Well, tomorrow's going to get better.

00:27:51.080 --> 00:27:52.280
' Why not now?

00:27:52.280 --> 00:27:56.560
Why not have your expiration date to what you're believing for now?

00:27:56.560 --> 00:28:04.173
Why not believe for the exceedingly abundantly above all that you would ask or think now?

00:28:04.173 --> 00:28:06.823
So, I'm believing for it tonight.

00:28:06.823 --> 00:28:09.107
I'm believing for it tomorrow.

00:28:09.107 --> 00:28:12.530
I'm believing right now.

00:28:12.530 --> 00:28:26.009
Let's just always stay in that constant state of being, in that constant state of believing that you receive it when you come together and you fellowship like that.

00:28:31.411 --> 00:28:31.646
And I thought, you know, it's a pull.

00:28:32.348 --> 00:28:33.840
You pull it.

00:28:35.387 --> 00:28:35.540
You can pull it.

00:28:35.540 --> 00:28:51.875
And it was cool because Sister Lynn was talking about praying for North Korea today and getting over in those rivers and praying, because, you know, she said it was interesting—I love her illustrations—she was talking about how there's no pictures, there's really no information about North Korea because it's so closed off.

00:28:58.925 --> 00:28:59.380
It's a wall.

00:28:59.380 --> 00:29:09.230
But as you pray into something, she said she takes her notebook and she writes everything about North Korea, what she's getting about that in prayer.

00:29:11.240 --> 00:29:19.720
And after a while, she has notebooks full, a prayer journal of everything that she has gotten from the Holy Spirit concerning North Korea.

00:29:19.720 --> 00:29:58.080
So I have gotten all this stuff about North Korea and praying into that, about what the Lord has told us—that He was going to remove a tyrant, that He was going to remove Kim Jong-un, and that his days were numbered, that his sister's days were numbered, that God was going to give North Korea a window of opportunity for a major outpouring of the Spirit of God, and that there would be a great harvest of souls in the days to come concerning North Korea and South Korea and China and basically all of Asia.

00:30:11.400 --> 00:30:11.550
And He said, 'We're going to have a major move of God in Asia.

00:30:11.550 --> 00:30:12.967
' So that's what we're believing for.

00:30:12.967 --> 00:30:15.430
He said, 'I have not forgotten my Asians.

00:30:19.530 --> 00:30:19.800
I have not forgotten the Asians.

00:30:19.800 --> 00:30:22.051
They have felt that they have been forgotten.

00:30:22.051 --> 00:30:32.640
' But the Lord said, 'Brandon, I have not forgotten my Asians, and there is going to be the greatest harvest of souls that they've ever experienced, ever in all of time, that Asia will have a move of God.

00:30:32.640 --> 00:30:34.971
' And that's what we're believing for.

00:30:34.971 --> 00:30:41.208
So, going back to—I don't want to get sidetracked—going back to the Tomahawks now, President Trump right now is negotiating and talking about sending some long-range missiles into there, trying to stiff-arm Putin.

00:30:52.809 --> 00:30:53.004
And I said, 'Don't poke the bear.

00:30:53.004 --> 00:31:00.080
' Remember, every single thing we're getting: don't poke the bear, don't send these long-range missiles.

00:31:13.169 --> 00:31:14.262
So, as we're praying into that, I believe we can stop some of that to delay it and make it not happen, because this is going to be very bad for Poland and Romania and some of these other nations.

00:31:22.640 --> 00:31:27.010
But as we see the enemy within the Red Dawn experience, the Lord said, 'We must pray for America because of what I saw yesterday concerning the major building that was on fire at the top.

00:31:27.010 --> 00:31:30.658
' And He said, 'This is the distraction from the main thing.

00:31:38.240 --> 00:31:38.556
This building was to attract the firefighters, the emergency crew responders, from the main event.

00:31:38.556 --> 00:31:51.520
' And I saw tripwires in buildings that were booby-trapped, that when the firefighters walked in, it was over—that they were rigged for a catastrophic event on purpose to delay and to cause a distraction from what they're trying to do over at another place.

00:31:51.520 --> 00:31:54.400
Does that make sense, what I'm trying to tell y'all?

00:31:54.400 --> 00:31:55.394
It was a deterrent.

00:31:55.394 --> 00:31:56.742
That's a good word, a deterrent.

00:32:07.543 --> 00:32:07.840
So, that's what we're going to pray into a little bit more today in this little bit of time that we have left here.

00:32:16.338 --> 00:32:16.733
So, I hope I gave you a little bit of something to get you excited.

00:32:16.733 --> 00:32:18.373
It's time, folks.

00:32:31.756 --> 00:32:32.634
I want you to have an expectation that God is going to show up and show off in your life.

00:32:32.634 --> 00:32:35.270
Have expectation.

00:32:35.280 --> 00:32:46.060
It's not just Brandon, it's not just Diana or Billy or Lynn or Pastor Chip or Candace or whoever, it's you.

00:32:46.060 --> 00:32:47.895
God has a plan for you.

00:32:47.895 --> 00:32:49.720
God has a plan to do something for you.

00:32:49.720 --> 00:33:06.590
You might live in some hole-in-the-wall, this little podunk town in America, or in Australia or whatever, and you've got less than a population of a thousand people, and you're going, 'How is God going to do anything in this little bitty town with less than 500 people in it?

00:33:06.590 --> 00:33:18.956
' But you're there and you're watching online right now, and you're praying for your town, and you could be the one that brings revival to save that whole entire little village, that whole entire little town.

00:33:21.760 --> 00:33:22.780
And you are the one that carries the fire.

00:33:25.651 --> 00:33:25.960
And you go, 'Why did God place me here?

00:33:25.960 --> 00:33:28.380
' Because you are called to those people.

00:33:29.260 --> 00:33:29.480
You never know.

00:33:29.480 --> 00:33:33.098
Maybe He's telling you to move on.

00:33:33.098 --> 00:33:38.937
Maybe He's telling you it's time to pack your bags and move into a big city.

00:33:47.948 --> 00:33:58.971
I don't know, but I know that God put you where you are right now, maybe just for this season, just for—you're called to the Kingdom for such a time as this.

00:34:07.352 --> 00:34:07.568
And it could be there just for that, for a major revival in that little town, and you're the first one.

00:34:07.568 --> 00:34:09.320
All it takes is—how to start a fire?

00:34:09.320 --> 00:34:10.520
It just takes a spark.

00:34:14.840 --> 00:34:15.022
And you could be the spark that lights that fire.

00:34:19.351 --> 00:34:19.528
Just know that nothing's by coincidence.

00:34:19.528 --> 00:34:21.220
You're there and God has you.

00:34:30.800 --> 00:34:31.060
You can say, 'Well, everybody, all they do over here is do drugs and sleep around and everything, drinking at the bars on Friday nights, and we don't ever have any...

00:34:31.060 --> 00:34:41.149
' You could be the one that starts a Holy Ghost fire in there and has a tent revival or your little church, and you're feeling it, and the Holy Ghost shows up.

00:34:41.149 --> 00:34:50.355
I thought, you know, when I told Diana—we were talking about it—what attracts us to these meetings, going to healing services like Billye's and Billy, both Billys, is the anointing.

00:34:52.106 --> 00:34:52.351
All it takes is a spark.

00:35:09.160 --> 00:35:09.560
All it takes is that tangible.

00:35:18.580 --> 00:35:18.840
You couldn't pull me away from it.

00:35:18.840 --> 00:35:21.343
I'm like a dog on a bone.

00:35:21.343 --> 00:35:22.933
That's what it takes.

00:35:24.743 --> 00:35:27.700
And I thought, how did you get that?

00:35:27.700 --> 00:35:28.491
By spending time.

00:35:28.491 --> 00:35:28.994
T-I-M-E.

00:35:28.994 --> 00:35:29.497
Time.

00:35:29.497 --> 00:35:33.220
That's what sitting at the feet of the Father with time brings: relationship.

00:35:34.576 --> 00:35:40.687
And I thought—Diana and I talk about it—there's no microwave.

00:35:40.687 --> 00:35:47.640
It's a slow cooker.

00:35:47.640 --> 00:35:56.120
It's relationship, just like you have with—you don't force your relationship with your spouse.

00:35:56.120 --> 00:35:59.833
What develops a relationship with your wife or with your husband?

00:36:14.218 --> 00:36:14.422
Time.

00:36:14.422 --> 00:36:18.680
Well, 'I want—we've got to have a crash course right now.

00:36:19.075 --> 00:36:23.147
I want to know everything about you in the next 10 minutes.

00:36:23.147 --> 00:36:43.271
You're going to tell me everything from your childhood, and I want you to tell me, and I'm going to time it, and then you're going to tell me, and then I'm going to know everything about you, and then we're going to be so good with each other.

00:36:43.271 --> 00:36:45.400
' That wouldn't work, would it?

00:36:45.400 --> 00:36:48.680
She'd look at me and go, 'Are you kidding me?

00:36:48.680 --> 00:36:49.730
This is not a microwave.

00:36:49.730 --> 00:36:50.900
It has taken time, years.

00:36:50.900 --> 00:36:55.000
' And I still find out stuff all the time.

00:37:02.686 --> 00:37:02.977
We talk about things and you go, 'Okay, well, I like your likes and your dislikes and everything else.

00:37:02.977 --> 00:37:05.520
' But that's the way it is with the Lord.

00:37:09.062 --> 00:37:09.267
But it's by refiner's fire.

00:37:12.440 --> 00:37:12.795
And we come up higher every day.

00:37:16.051 --> 00:37:16.206
And you come up higher with the fire.

00:37:16.693 --> 00:37:20.127
And every day you go from glory to glory to glory.

00:39:30.360 --> 00:39:30.613
And people want something quick.

00:39:44.714 --> 00:39:45.160
And that's why I told Brianna, I'm willing to pay the price to get whatever it takes to get there—meetings like this, dipping in the river, praying, doing these videos, doing whatever it takes because I want Him.

00:39:45.160 --> 00:39:50.120
What does it take to get the manifested presence with Him?

00:39:50.120 --> 00:39:54.954
We know that that's what breaks the yoke, that's what sets people free.

00:39:54.954 --> 00:39:57.080
None of this other stuff.

00:39:57.080 --> 00:40:01.440
You go into a church service and you just—I don't want church usual.

00:40:08.653 --> 00:40:09.000
I want church unusual.

00:40:17.610 --> 00:40:17.800
You get something when you go, and you don't walk away going, 'What was that?

00:40:17.800 --> 00:40:19.356
I'm wasting my time.

00:40:19.356 --> 00:40:22.013
' I want His presence.

00:40:22.013 --> 00:40:25.504
When you go, man, 'Father, thank you for that fresh drink.

00:40:25.504 --> 00:40:29.933
' But I don't rely on my pastors to bring that to me all the time.

00:40:42.436 --> 00:40:42.720
I get it myself.

00:40:51.613 --> 00:40:52.187
You get it yourself.

00:40:52.187 --> 00:40:55.933
How desperate, how bad do you want change in your life?

00:40:55.933 --> 00:41:02.480
I don't sit there and go, 'Well, it's like a baby wanting their diaper changed.

00:41:02.480 --> 00:41:09.472
' After you grow up, you don't have to have your diaper changed anymore because you've grown up.

00:41:09.472 --> 00:41:18.450
Well, I don't have to have somebody feed me anymore because I feed myself.

00:41:18.450 --> 00:41:22.040
Well, I learned how to cook myself.

00:41:22.040 --> 00:41:25.810
I learned how to do that.

00:41:26.730 --> 00:41:28.724
The older you get, the further along with the Lord you get.

00:41:41.836 --> 00:41:41.991
I'm able to go say, 'You know what?

00:41:56.370 --> 00:41:56.685
I know how to go to the drive-thru if I need to.

00:42:13.533 --> 00:42:14.889
I know how to go to the grocery store and fix it, but I don't have to go by and say, Mom, Dad, I need you to go and get me something because I'm hungry.

00:42:14.889 --> 00:42:18.200
' They're saying, 'You're an adult.

00:42:18.200 --> 00:42:19.900
Go get it yourself.

00:42:19.900 --> 00:42:25.030
' You know what I'm saying?

00:42:31.343 --> 00:42:31.514
That's the way it is.

00:42:32.680 --> 00:42:57.255
I really truly believe, the more you grow spiritually, it's time for a lot of people to grow up and stop being babies.

00:42:57.255 --> 00:43:19.170
We've got to get our armor on and get ready for what's coming.

00:43:19.170 --> 00:43:21.880
Most people don't want to recognize it.

00:43:21.880 --> 00:43:26.600
Most people are afraid of it.

00:43:26.600 --> 00:43:28.360
What's coming?

00:43:28.360 --> 00:43:58.022
Do I believe it?

00:44:12.040 --> 00:44:13.480
It's like I see part of the charismatic movement—I want to say the Word of Faith people—they are so strong on, 'We're not going to experience anything at all.

00:44:13.480 --> 00:44:24.800
We're underneath the glory and the glory's coming because this prophet said this and that prophet said that,' but I'm telling you we are in this world.

00:44:37.600 --> 00:44:37.960
I know we're not of it, but we're going to see some things.

00:44:46.880 --> 00:44:47.080
But it doesn't have to be—I'm not going to participate in the drama, right?

00:44:50.000 --> 00:44:50.587
So I know the glory is on my household.

00:44:50.587 --> 00:44:55.680
And as He is, so are we in this world.

00:44:55.680 --> 00:45:07.069
And as Diana and I walk into the world, we touch and shed the light, but we're still going to see it.

00:45:07.069 --> 00:45:09.880
It doesn't make it disappear.

00:45:09.880 --> 00:45:15.320
It just means I'm not going to get into the drama of it.

00:45:21.555 --> 00:45:21.810
The sky is not falling in my house.

00:45:21.810 --> 00:46:25.584
It may be falling out there, but it ain't falling because why?

00:46:25.584 --> 00:46:30.680
Because the Holy Ghost is dwelling on the inside of me and He's giving me authority.

00:46:30.680 --> 00:46:35.840
Now, we know that in Matthew 24, these things are going to happen.

00:46:35.840 --> 00:46:38.850
This is the beginning of sorrows.

00:46:38.850 --> 00:46:42.360
So, you're not going to stop that.

00:46:42.360 --> 00:46:45.800
There's going to be plagues.

00:46:45.800 --> 00:46:48.200
There's going to be wars.

00:46:48.200 --> 00:46:50.749
There's going to be rumors of wars.

00:46:50.749 --> 00:46:54.944
So, we're going to see these things, civil unrest, these things.

00:46:54.944 --> 00:46:58.046
But where are we supposed to be?

00:46:58.046 --> 00:47:03.080
We're supposed to be in that position of, 'Hey, we have our catcher's mitts on, people.

00:47:03.080 --> 00:47:04.451
Hey, you need Jesus.

00:47:04.451 --> 00:47:06.653
Can I pray for you?

00:47:06.653 --> 00:47:07.880
Fear not.

00:47:07.880 --> 00:47:09.080
Fear not.

00:47:09.080 --> 00:47:11.220
' So, praise God.

00:47:11.220 --> 00:47:15.030
I'm not afraid and neither is anybody else.

00:47:15.030 --> 00:47:18.973
But I'm going to tell you, I know what's coming.

00:47:21.170 --> 00:47:24.120
And the glory is coming and it'll be as thick as a quarter.

00:47:24.120 --> 00:47:27.753
I've tried to say it a thousand times.

00:47:29.915 --> 00:47:33.825
The dark's going to get darker and the light is going to get lighter.

00:47:36.920 --> 00:47:42.920
We are in the last of the last days and we're fixing to see even more, a greater acceleration of things than we've ever seen before.

00:47:42.920 --> 00:47:45.973
So, Father, I just thank you.

00:47:45.973 --> 00:47:48.455
I don't have communion today.

00:47:48.455 --> 00:47:50.520
I ran out of communion.

00:47:50.520 --> 00:47:52.525
My wife brought me one for travel.

00:47:52.525 --> 00:47:54.800
So, we're just going to pray.

00:47:54.800 --> 00:47:58.845
Father, I thank you, Lord, as you show me.

00:47:58.845 --> 00:48:02.800
I plead the blood of Jesus over my eyes.

00:48:06.149 --> 00:48:08.957
And I thank you, Lord, that we have angels that keep charge over me.

00:48:14.160 --> 00:48:15.511
And anything and everything that I see, Father, I judge it.

00:48:17.105 --> 00:48:18.800
And I thank you, Lord.

00:48:18.800 --> 00:48:34.870
Hey, I can do it with a chip.

00:48:34.880 --> 00:48:36.700
That'll work.

00:48:36.700 --> 00:48:41.560
I'll take it with a chip.

00:48:44.375 --> 00:48:44.945
And just give me some of that sparkling tea right there.

00:48:44.945 --> 00:48:45.800
That tea.

00:48:45.800 --> 00:48:47.510
That'll work.

00:49:05.290 --> 00:49:05.560
We have lots at home now.

00:49:05.560 --> 00:49:08.765
But I'm in a hotel room.

00:49:08.765 --> 00:49:11.320
So, I want to clarify that.

00:49:11.320 --> 00:49:13.800
I'm not saying I don't have communion.

00:49:23.110 --> 00:49:23.415
I have communion, but I don't have it at the hotel.

00:49:23.415 --> 00:49:25.434
So, this will work today.

00:49:37.600 --> 00:49:37.880
This will work.

00:49:37.880 --> 00:49:39.000
You forgive me?

00:49:39.000 --> 00:49:41.875
I'm not trying to be disrespectful to Catholics.

00:49:41.875 --> 00:49:43.520
I'm not trying to be disrespectful.

00:49:56.969 --> 00:49:57.200
You know, I have a lot of people from a lot of different backgrounds and they got really offended when I did this last time.

00:49:57.200 --> 00:50:00.240
I'm not trying to be disrespectful.

00:50:00.240 --> 00:50:02.800
So, Father, I thank you, Father, for the body.

00:50:11.440 --> 00:50:11.760
And we take this body in the name of Jesus.

00:50:21.080 --> 00:50:21.360
And we thank you, Lord, that you see my heart.

00:50:21.360 --> 00:50:26.000
I'm just doing the best I can with what I have here.

00:50:26.000 --> 00:50:31.200
I'm doing the best I can with what I have here.

00:50:41.217 --> 00:50:41.686
And I'm so grateful, Father, for your body that was broken for us as we're in this hotel room.

00:50:41.686 --> 00:50:46.782
I thank you, Lord, that you were wounded for our transgressions.

00:50:56.720 --> 00:50:56.940
You were bruised for our iniquities.

00:51:08.130 --> 00:51:08.340
The chastisement of our peace was upon you.

00:51:26.260 --> 00:51:26.840
And with your stripes, we're healed.

00:51:40.520 --> 00:51:44.235
And as we pray for the next 30 minutes, Lord, we're thankful that if there is anything we can do to help change things, God, we can get a lot done with what we have here.

00:52:17.560 --> 00:52:18.007
And we take this body in the name of Jesus and we give you all the glory, honor, and praise.

00:52:20.240 --> 00:52:21.050
And Lord, we're thankful for the blood.

00:52:21.050 --> 00:52:24.711
We make much of the blood and the blood makes much of us.

00:52:24.947 --> 00:52:27.371
And we apply the blood of Jesus over us.

00:52:27.371 --> 00:52:33.851
We apply the blood of Jesus all around this hotel room.

00:52:33.851 --> 00:52:36.000
We apply the blood of Jesus over their houses.

00:52:36.640 --> 00:52:43.100
And we thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against us will prosper.

00:52:43.460 --> 00:52:45.920
And we plead the blood over everything you've been showing us.

00:52:49.120 --> 00:52:49.417
And we thank you, Lord.

